                     <interp inst="t18221023-95-person1021" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a pawnbroker. On the 9th of October, Valour pawned the spoon.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18221023-95-person1022">
                  GEORGE 
                  VALOUR
               <interp inst="t18221023-95-person1022" type="surname" value="VALOUR"></interp>
